		<br><br>
		TopCoder reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to revoke any and all privileges associated with competing in the challenge, and to take any other action it deems appropriate, for no reason or any reason whatsoever, including if TopCoder suspects competitors of cheating, tampering with the entry process, the operation of the Web site, or the challenge process, or otherwise being in violation of the rules. TopCoder reserves the right to cancel, terminate or modify the challenge if it is not capable of completion as planned for any reason, including infection by computer virus, bugs, tampering, unauthorized intervention or technical failures of any sort.
